            released, we will rely on the community to make the information as accurate and complete as possible. People
            who consistently contibute quality content will be recognized. 
        </li>
        <li>
            <b>Graphics, icons, design ...</b>
            We're looking for talented artists!
        </li>
        <li>
            <b>Codewalkers</b>
            Code help is always welcome: frontend, backend, or whatever end ;) Have a MTG tool you are working on 
